Cavani: &quot;I called Ander (Herrera) to have a chat. I have a lot of admiration for Ander, for the kind of person he is and I had the feeling that his words were going to help ne out, by telling me a bit about what it was like at Manchester United.&quot;<br />
<br />
Cavani: &quot;After I&rsquo;d finished talking with Ander (Herrera), we came to an agreement here with the club. I hadn&rsquo;t known Ander for too long, but we formed and enjoyed a close friendship during that time at PSG, and today we are still very good mates.&quot;

